SubjectBy-elections (3) - Vaughan, Winnipeg-North, Dauphin--Swan River--Marquette
PrecisOrder directing that WRITS OF ELECTION do issue in order to fill the vacancies in the House of Commons for the electoral districts of WINNIPEG NORTH (Manitoba), VAUGHAN (Ontario), and DAUPHIN--SWAN RIVER-- MARQUETTE (Manitoba), with polling to take place on November 29, 2010.
